         <div type="translation" resp="#jmr" xml:lang="en">
            <p> <note>a</note> To Publius Septimius Geta, most noble Caesar <note>all erased</note> the colony of Septimia Tyre, metropolis of Phoenicia and of other cities. <note>b</note> Septimius Heraclitus, saw to the erection.</p></div>
         <div type="commentary">
